scene.message:
{color:2}Yamaoka{nl}
The Nanjo family butler.{nl}
Has looked after Nanjo{nl}
since he was a child.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: Oh my goodness!{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Young master Kei has come{nl}
home with his friends!{nl}
I am so pleased~!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Y-Yamaoka!{nl}
How many times must I say{nl}
stop calling me that!?{waitkey}{nl}
I am...{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: Oh my!{nl}
Are you going out{nl}
with everyone, young master!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: We're just going to{nl}
the hospital! And stop{nl}
calling me young master!{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: My goodness!{nl}
The hospital, you say!{nl}
Are you injured, young master!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I'm done with this!{nl}
Let's go, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Yamaoka, do NOT follow us!{waitkey}{ret}
